item.title: mongodb4.2 ARM平台编译
item.author: 作者
item.description: mongodb4.2 ARM平台编 1.Gcc和依赖软件下载 1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8 9 wget https://gcc.gnu.org/pub/gcc/infrastructure/gmp-6.1.0.tar.bz2 wget https://gcc.gnu.org/pub/gcc/infrastructure/mpfr-3.1.4.tar.bz2 wget https://gcc.gnu.org/pub/gcc/infrastructure/mpc-1.0.3.tar.gz wget https://gcc.gnu.org/pub/gcc/infrastructure/isl-0.18.tar.bz2 wget https://gcc.gnu.org/pub/gcc/releases/gcc-9.2.0/gcc-9.2.0.tar.gz 2.下载mongodb源码包 1 wget https://fastdl.mongodb.org/src/mongodb-src-r4.2.8.tar.gz 将1、2的软件包上传到/opt
